Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.90,0:00:07.44,CG ON,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,The Britannian youth, Lelouch, has embarked on two paths.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.03,0:00:12.36,CG ON,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,One is to find his mother's enemy. A path that leads to the "past".
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.36,0:00:19.11,CG ON,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,The other is to turn the world into a place that his sister, Nunnally, can live in happily. A path that leads to the "future".
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.12,0:00:23.16,CG ON,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,As Lelouch gazes at both the "past" and the "future",
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.16,0:00:26.01,CG ON,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,is the path that leads to the "present", which only he can choose,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.01,0:00:27.96,CG ON,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,the destruction of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.96,0:00:30.00,CG ON,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,or the reconstruction of the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.62,0:02:19.43,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,550)}In the past, we had problems even getting a bike, but now a submarine...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.43,0:02:22.54,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Although this is the Indian Armed Forces's military zone, it'll still be bad if we get discovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.54,0:02:25.16,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,What route are we taking? That woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.16,0:02:30.54,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, I'm going to announce the new organization chart resulting from the reorganization of the Order of the Black Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.54,0:02:33.59,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,The overall in-charge for military affairs will be Tohdoh Kyoshiro. {Official Romanisation...}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.88,0:02:40.80,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,The overall in-charge for all aspects of intelligence, including publicity, spying and public relations will be Diethard Ried.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.25,0:02:43.01,CG ON,Tamaki,0000,0000,0000,,The Britannian here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.01,0:02:44.60,CG ON,Urabe,0000,0000,0000,,He's from the media too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.11,0:02:50.62,CG ON,Nagisa,0000,0000,0000,,Zero, I'm not trying to be racist, but what is your reason for intentionally appointing a Britannian?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.62,0:02:51.35,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.88,0:02:53.52,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Then what about myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.28,0:02:57.37,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,As you all know, I'm not Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.37,0:03:00.47,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,What is needed is the ability to produce results.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.47,0:03:03.78,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Things like race, personal history, and methods don't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.78,0:03:04.99,CG ON,Tamaki,0000,0000,0000,,I get it. I get it already.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.26,0:03:07.95,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,The vice commander will be Ohgi Kaname. {Official Romanization...}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.37,0:03:09.18,CG ON,Ohgi,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.18,0:03:10.23,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Not happy with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.23,0:03:11.43,CG ON,Ohgi,0000,0000,0000,,N-No...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.43,0:03:14.23,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the original leader was Ohgi after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.23,0:03:15.69,CG ON,???02,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be a bit improper if it were assigned to some newcomer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.21,0:03:18.65,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,The chief of technological research and development will be Rakshata.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.65,0:03:19.24,CG ON,Rakshata,0000,0000,0000,,Obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.79,0:03:22.29,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,The commander of Team Zero will be Kohzuki Kallen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.29,0:03:22.97,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Team Zero?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.42,0:03:26.09,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Only Team Zero will come under my direct control.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.09,0:03:28.56,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Just think of it as my personal unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.56,0:03:30.79,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Zero's... personal unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.98,0:03:33.89,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,The commander of Team One will be Asahina Shogo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.89,0:03:36.32,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,The commander of Team Two will be Senba Ryoga.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.32,0:03:38.84,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,The commander of Team Three will be Kagezaki Kizuna.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.32,0:03:46.71,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,The commander of the second special forces team will be Tamaki Shinichiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.71,0:03:47.18,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.18,0:03:47.91,CG ON,Tamaki,0000,0000,0000,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.91,0:03:48.94,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.38,0:03:51.58,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,C.C. isn't assigned any posts.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.08,0:03:56.76,CG ON,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,Zero, mind if I ask a question?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.76,0:03:57.21,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.21,0:04:00.80,CG ON,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,There's an agenda that I wish to discuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.25,0:04:05.15,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Even though he is a honorary Britannian, for an Eleven to become a knight is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.15,0:04:07.01,CG ON,???02,0000,0000,0000,,It's already been confirmed and announced on television.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.01,0:04:08.60,CG ON,???03,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how he got through...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.91,0:04:12.36,CG ON,???04,0000,0000,0000,,Guess it's due to love. Princess Euphemia is at that age after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.23,0:04:16.46,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.46,0:04:17.65,CG ON,???02,0000,0000,0000,,This shouldn't be possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.89,0:04:20.26,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,An Eleven as a major...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.26,0:04:21.32,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Kururugi Suzaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.73,0:04:27.53,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Art thou willing to stand by the knight's covenant and fight as a Britannian Knight?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.53,0:04:29.28,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Your Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.55,0:04:35.87,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Art thou willing to forsake thy desires and act as our sword and shield for the sake of greater justice?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.38,0:04:38.25,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Your Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.35,0:04:58.52,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,I, Euphemia Li Britannia, acknowledge thee, Kururugi Suzaku, as a knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.91,0:04:59.72,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Bravery...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.72,0:05:01.67,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,His affiliation is becoming complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.67,0:05:04.20,CG ON,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like Lloyd-san managed to convince him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.20,0:05:05.21,CG ON,???01,0000,0000,0000,,That person?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.21,0:05:08.12,CG ON,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Even though I've yet to meet him...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.53,0:05:56.33,CG ON,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,Kururugi Suzaku... he is like a banner to the Elevens who wish to pledge their allegiance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.58,0:05:58.54,CG ON,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,I propose that we assassinate him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.98,0:06:01.07,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Assassinate...? Kururugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.07,0:06:02.52,CG ON,Rakshata,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.52,0:06:07.37,CG ON,Rakshata,0000,0000,0000,,There's Zero who's like a star for those who want to revolt, but there isn't one for those who want to pledge their allegiance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.37,0:06:10.24,CG ON,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,People won't act just for principles or opinions.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.24,0:06:14.19,CG ON,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,Now that someone symbolic has appeared in Britannia,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.19,0:06:17.54,CG ON,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,I think assassination is the most realistic measure we could take...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.54,0:06:18.48,CG ON,Tohdoh,0000,0000,0000,,I object.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.48,0:06:22.11,CG ON,Tohdoh,0000,0000,0000,,You won't gain the support of the Japanese through the use of such despicable methods.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.55,0:06:26.49,CG ON,Ohgi,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. We, the Order of the Black Knights, will not kill an unarmed person.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.85,0:06:31.38,CG ON,Ohgi,0000,0000,0000,,Assassination means... that we kill him during his private moments when he is not armed, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.38,0:06:36.63,CG ON,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just proposing the most realistic measure with the least risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.63,0:06:39.48,CG ON,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1000)}Zero is the one to make the decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.48,0:06:41.15,CG ON,C.C.,0000,0000,0000,,This is easy, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.15,0:06:43.96,CG ON,C.C.,0000,0000,0000,,You just need to use your Geass on Kururugi Suzaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.96,0:06:44.42,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.69,0:06:45.61,CG ON,C.C.,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.61,0:06:49.17,CG ON,C.C.,0000,0000,0000,,Stubbornness? Friendship? Or pride?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.15,0:06:52.12,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.12,0:06:54.60,CG ON,C.C.,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it means killing him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.16,0:06:59.86,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,You're remaining silent...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.86,0:07:02.66,CG ON,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,Appointing knights is a special right of the royalty.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.66,0:07:05.58,CG ON,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I'm the Govenor-General, I can't intervene in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.58,0:07:12.09,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Kururugi Suzaku may only be an honorary Britannian, but his capabilities match those expected of a knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.09,0:07:12.98,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Also, Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.98,0:07:13.62,CG ON,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,Governor-General.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.71,0:07:17.74,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Governor-General, you should have seen that yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.74,0:07:20.76,CG ON,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,Treating Numbers differently is a national policy of Britannia.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.76,0:07:22.79,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll try and change that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.81,0:07:27.21,CG ON,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what that means, Vice Governor-General?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.51,0:07:30.06,CG ON,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,It means that you wish to be the Emperor!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.28,0:07:37.47,CG ON,Emperor,0000,0000,0000,,The construction of the thought elevator is going as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.47,0:07:40.06,CG ON,Emperor,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.40,0:07:44.93,CG ON,Emperor,0000,0000,0000,,Schneiser is...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.93,0:07:46.77,CG ON,Aide,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.98,0:07:49.85,CG ON,Emperor,0000,0000,0000,,Let him do as he wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.85,0:07:52.72,CG ON,Emperor,0000,0000,0000,,He can challenge me if he's confident.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.72,0:07:59.62,CG ON,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,With that, to commemorate our Ashford Academy Student Council's disciplinary member, Kururugi Suzaku, in becoming a knight...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.12,0:08:01.79,CG ON,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,The start of the celebration party!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.07,0:08:03.58,CG ON,Rest,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.58,0:08:05.47,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, you sure are amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.47,0:08:07.21,CG ON,???02,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations, Suzaku-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.21,0:08:09.92,CG ON,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,The one who planned and drafted this out was Nunnally.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.92,0:08:14.45,CG ON,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that many people have already congratulated you, but are you still willing to accept our congratulations?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.45,0:08:16.47,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Of course. I'm very happy now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.73,0:08:24.39,CG ON,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,What... What should I do...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.39,0:08:26.04,CG ON,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Euphemia...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.04,0:08:27.77,CG ON,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,Good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.77,0:08:32.11,CG ON,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,You there, where is Major Kururugi Suzaku? They said that he was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.41,0:08:35.53,CG ON,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to be doing something interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.77,0:08:37.02,CG ON,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,You understand this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.02,0:08:39.98,CG ON,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,Uranium, right? The one with an isotope mass of 235.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.98,0:08:41.76,CG ON,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.76,0:08:45.07,CG ON,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,If the uranium-235 undergoes thermal neutron absorption,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.07,0:08:48.46,CG ON,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,it will split into two nuclei and release free neutrons.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.46,0:08:51.72,CG ON,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,However, the problem is the source material, the uranium-235.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.72,0:08:55.02,CG ON,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,They only make up 0.7% of all the uranium naturally found.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.02,0:08:57.71,CG ON,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much effort we put into preparing the machine to split them up,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.71,0:09:00.06,CG ON,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,we are unable to conduct the actual experiment if it remains like this. That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.58,0:09:02.53,CG ON,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,President, where is Nina?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.53,0:09:03.98,CG ON,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,I asked her, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.16,0:09:18.47,CG ON,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Kallen!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.47,0:09:20.42,CG ON,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,Can you help out in arranging the pizzas?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.15,0:09:29.17,CG ON,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.53,0:09:31.57,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Kallen, this is for Zero's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.42,0:09:34.21,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't do it here...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.05,0:09:39.45,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Shirley said that she wanted you to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.45,0:09:43.07,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. There's something important that I have to do now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.07,0:09:44.68,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,What is that "something important"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.56,0:09:46.59,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.04,0:09:48.48,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.22,0:09:50.40,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.40,0:09:52.70,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy just to see you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.20,0:09:55.17,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yes, about the thing you wanted to tell me the other day?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.17,0:09:57.50,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Remember? You said there was something important.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.50,0:10:00.01,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that is... erm...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.01,0:10:00.95,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.95,0:10:01.75,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.26,0:10:06.71,CG ON,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but work has increased, Suzaku-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.03,0:10:08.47,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,A-Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.47,0:10:09.26,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.26,0:10:10.63,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,My superior.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.89,0:10:12.92,CG ON,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,Lloyd-san, what is it...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.92,0:10:15.26,CG ON,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Milly-chan, you know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.26,0:10:16.35,CG ON,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,I’m her fiancé.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.35,0:10:16.72,CG ON,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.72,0:10:18.13,CG ON,Rest,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.44,0:10:20.17,CG ON,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,Is that fine?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.17,0:10:21.93,CG ON,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,A-Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.93,0:10:23.43,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,He said it out loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.43,0:10:24.50,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,You knew about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.50,0:10:25.22,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.52,0:10:28.29,CG ON,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.29,0:10:30.41,CG ON,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,Then you are... What's his name?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.41,0:10:31.30,CG ON,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,Earl Lloyd.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.30,0:10:32.31,CG ON,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,Earl?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.31,0:10:34.24,CG ON,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,Erm... Mr. Earl...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.24,0:10:37.11,CG ON,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,Then how are the two of you related...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.11,0:10:38.35,CG ON,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve already said that I’m her fiancé.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.49,0:10:40.24,CG ON,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.66,0:10:42.19,CG ON,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,He was serious...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.19,0:10:44.53,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Erm... is it military work?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.81,0:10:48.18,CG ON,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. An important guest is arriving by ship and we need to receive him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.18,0:10:52.96,CG ON,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, the Lancelot and Her Highness Princess Euphemia need to be present.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.24,0:11:05.05,CG ON,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(670,0)\fs22\i1}Note: Shikinejima is a volcanic island located south of Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.24,0:11:05.05,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(670,0)}Why Shikinejima? The Tokyo settlement is much safer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.05,0:11:07.06,CG ON,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,I want to know the reason too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.06,0:11:09.75,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Cecile-san, you don't know about it either?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.75,0:11:10.64,CG ON,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,I don't either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.64,0:11:11.34,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.34,0:11:13.51,CG ON,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't we acting a bit carelessly?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.51,0:11:16.47,CG ON,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,Seems that our movement schedule has been posted on the Internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.47,0:11:19.55,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,There was an interesting girl, so I had to offer some lip service...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.12,0:11:24.77,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Euphemia is going to that island to receive an aristocrat who is coming from the main country.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.77,0:11:27.54,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Kururugi Suzaku will be going with her since he is her knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.90,0:11:31.50,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,As it isn't a place of any strategic value, the military power of the enemy should be limited.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.50,0:11:33.12,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,This is a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.12,0:11:37.49,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,The objective of this mission is to capture the Lancelot and Suzaku alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.49,0:11:40.17,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,We will defeat him fair and square in battle and turn him into our captive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.43,0:11:44.36,CG ON,Tamaki,0000,0000,0000,,What happens after he becomes our captive?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.36,0:11:47.01,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,After that, leave the rest to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.85,0:11:52.69,CG ON,Rakshata,0000,0000,0000,,So this area?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.98,0:11:54.72,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Will it go well?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.72,0:11:56.09,CG ON,Rakshata,0000,0000,0000,,It should be fine, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.09,0:11:59.11,CG ON,Rakshata,0000,0000,0000,,The stealth generated as a byproduct still seems to be operational.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.11,0:12:00.69,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.69,0:12:04.25,CG ON,Rakshata,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Britannia hasn't discovered us, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.25,0:12:05.28,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.74,0:12:08.24,CG ON,Rakshata,0000,0000,0000,,This is just the first step though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.24,0:12:09.75,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Diethard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.75,0:12:11.87,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,What were you trying to inspire Kallen to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.87,0:12:15.11,CG ON,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,I only wanted her to trail Kururugi Suzaku secretly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.11,0:12:17.04,CG ON,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,I only dropped her some small hints.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.53,0:12:19.26,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do anything without permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.26,0:12:21.76,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember ordering any assassinations.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.27,0:12:28.71,CG ON,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, it's fine as long as the people view it as a strike from the hammer of justice and not a despicable assassination, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.71,0:12:31.02,CG ON,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,We can use the media to conceal the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.08,0:12:35.79,CG ON,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,Nice words alone are not sufficient if you want to take over the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.79,0:12:36.94,CG ON,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,Am I mistaken?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.63,0:12:40.94,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Diethard, what are you trying to achieve?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.94,0:12:44.39,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you were demoted, you are still a Britannian.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.39,0:12:48.28,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,There isn't a need for you to change the world by following the Order of the Black Knights, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.28,0:12:53.83,CG ON,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,The first time I saw you during the Kururugi Suzaku extortion incident,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.94,0:12:55.77,CG ON,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,420)}I was moved.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.98,0:12:59.59,CG ON,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,480)}A new era assumed a human form and stood there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.92,0:13:01.71,CG ON,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,I want to film you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.21,0:13:07.72,CG ON,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,A lone man formed an organization to defeat a country and eventually reign over the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.72,0:13:10.93,CG ON,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,I want to record this in history at the closest distance possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.33,0:13:13.78,CG ON,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,There is nothing more emotionally moving than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.78,0:13:14.85,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Record?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.85,0:13:18.94,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,When you get involved in an incident, records will become fabricated.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.94,0:13:21.39,CG ON,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,There isn't a report that has no bias.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.39,0:13:26.11,CG ON,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,Zero, isn't journalism something created by the consciousness of the people?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.11,0:13:28.66,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,You are not in charge of military matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.66,0:13:30.37,CG ON,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.45,0:13:33.68,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,The arrival time will remain as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.68,0:13:36.92,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Headquarters has already prepared a room to rest in.\NWhat should we do next?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.38,0:13:40.18,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that the boat will be docking here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.18,0:13:41.88,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that hasn't been changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.88,0:13:43.30,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Then, let's wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.30,0:13:44.32,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.32,0:13:46.09,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,The one in charge of security is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.72,0:13:50.89,CG ON,???02,0000,0000,0000,,Terrorists?! How did they get here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.68,0:13:57.12,CG ON,Tohdoh,0000,0000,0000,,Team One, continue your advance forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.12,0:13:59.54,CG ON,Tohdoh,0000,0000,0000,,Team Zero will provide cover from behind Team One.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.82,0:14:00.71,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you, Elevens!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.28,0:14:08.13,CG ON,Shogo,0000,0000,0000,,That girl is unexpectedly good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.87,0:14:13.73,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,As expected from Tohdoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.73,0:14:17.77,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,420)}He defeated the Britannian army before without any KnightMares.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.77,0:14:21.17,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,All that's left is to get this information to Euphemia...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.75,0:14:24.21,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Headquarters seems to be under attack by someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.49,0:14:25.11,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.11,0:14:27.05,CG ON,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,Let's head back to the settlement.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.05,0:14:29.36,CG ON,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,Can you arrange for an escort?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.36,0:14:31.15,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,It might be more dangerous to return.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.15,0:14:34.60,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Communications jamming seems to be going on around this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.60,0:14:36.12,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.12,0:14:38.95,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,I will protect Princess Euphemia myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.95,0:14:42.22,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,No, I want you to provide assistance to headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.22,0:14:42.65,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.90,0:14:45.63,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Vice Govenor-General, he is an honorary Britannian.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.29,0:14:49.17,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Chances are high that the enemy is the Order of the Black Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.17,0:14:51.06,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,If Lancelot defects over...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.06,0:14:53.13,CG ON,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,Erm... do you know what you're saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.13,0:14:54.60,CG ON,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,You are criticizing royalty.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.49,0:14:57.87,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,No... that wasn't my intention...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.30,0:15:02.42,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Kururugi Suzaku, you shall demonstrate your capabilities here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.42,0:15:05.04,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,By doing that, those criticisms will eventually disappear, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.30,0:15:06.11,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Madam.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.11,0:15:11.41,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,You're just the defense force!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.47,0:15:16.44,CG ON,Tamaki,0000,0000,0000,,I will deal the final blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.82,0:15:27.94,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Zero... it is indeed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.21,0:15:30.70,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Come, charge towards me, Suzaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.21,0:15:33.28,CG ON,Tohdoh,0000,0000,0000,,Confirming the target.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.80,0:15:36.20,CG ON,Tohdoh,0000,0000,0000,,All units, maintain formation three and retreat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.65,0:15:38.17,CG ON,Tohdoh,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do anything to the target.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.17,0:15:40.16,CG ON,Tohdoh,0000,0000,0000,,I repeat: Don't do anything to the target!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.40,0:15:42.75,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... All thanks to the special envoy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.75,0:15:45.06,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,But th-that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.11,0:15:47.77,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Your Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.85,0:15:56.59,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,To actually jump onto sand without any special equipment on...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.59,0:16:00.70,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Is he intending to get the Lancelot surrounded by using himself as bait?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.00,0:16:01.71,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.90,0:16:09.32,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Zero, with this...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.32,0:16:09.98,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,You...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.28,0:16:10.92,CG ON,Rakshata,0000,0000,0000,,Have been captured.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.84,0:16:19.82,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.09,0:16:23.89,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,I can't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.60,0:16:29.64,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,It's useless?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.64,0:16:32.09,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I have something to tell you, Kururugi Suzaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.78,0:16:34.51,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Mind coming out?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.51,0:16:36.53,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Everything except for the first propulsion system should still be operational.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.47,0:16:40.48,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I will be following international laws in terms of how to treat captives.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.48,0:16:44.81,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,If you are not willing to listen, you will be shot from all four directions.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.48,0:16:50.14,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right! Tell Suzaku to go out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.14,0:16:52.99,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, why is the Lancelot not moving?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.30,0:16:58.46,CG ON,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,Something is interfering with the reaction of the Sakuradite that is inside the KnightMare's propulsion system.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.46,0:16:59.95,CG ON,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,Gefjun Disturber.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.95,0:17:00.88,CG ON,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.88,0:17:03.41,CG ON,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,But part of the cause is due to the jamming that is going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.80,0:17:06.54,CG ON,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that it would continue to exist only in theory... \NI was too careless.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.03,0:17:09.63,CG ON,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,So it really is you, Rakshata.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.63,0:17:12.80,CG ON,Rakshata,0000,0000,0000,,The effective radius and operation time is still not ideal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.40,0:17:18.65,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Kururugi Suzaku, I will be blunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.65,0:17:20.80,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to be one of my comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.80,0:17:22.01,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Is this a threat?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.46,0:17:24.13,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, I refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.13,0:17:28.60,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,I told you before. It's worthless to achieve results using the wrong methods.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.91,0:17:30.22,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Then I ask you,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.22,0:17:32.32,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,is the peace we have now meaningless?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.33,0:17:38.46,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think would have happened if Japan chose to adopt a do-or-die resistance seven years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.99,0:17:43.53,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,The Chinese Federation and the EU would have intervened, and Japan would have been divided in three.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.53,0:17:45.83,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Battles would be breaking out even now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.83,0:17:50.42,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, the peace we have now is the product of that immediate unconditional surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.98,0:17:57.43,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,That's right... I'm fighting to prevent the peace that Father created from collapsing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.68,0:18:00.53,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,No, you are mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.53,0:18:04.22,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,The surrender was not the decision of the elected Prime Minister Kururugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.22,0:18:06.71,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,It was something selfishly decided by someone who killed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.95,0:18:12.86,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,The command authority of the government was thrown into confusion and they had no choice but to surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.86,0:18:16.39,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand? The will of the people was stolen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.39,0:18:19.95,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Selfishly! By that single culprit who broke the rule!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.38,0:18:21.50,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Can you hear them?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.50,0:18:23.49,CG ON,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,The microphone is picking up too much noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.54,0:18:26.85,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Why... That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.85,0:18:29.81,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,There is only one means for atonement.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.81,0:18:30.42,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.69,0:18:35.99,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Support, with all your effort, the choice that the Japanese were unable to make then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.99,0:18:39.97,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,The path that was taken away seven years ago... To fight against Britannia.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.97,0:18:41.64,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Fight? That again?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.44,0:18:44.41,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,This is another path to take.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.41,0:18:49.90,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Do you intend to spread that ego of yours to everyone for eternity?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.90,0:18:51.56,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Is that what you call peace?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.49,0:18:54.69,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,E..mer...gen...cy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.69,0:18:56.57,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Can you hear me, Major Kururugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.57,0:18:57.52,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.52,0:18:58.29,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Can I?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.29,0:18:59.26,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Do as you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.81,0:19:03.71,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,This is Colonel Harry, the commander of Britannia's Shikinejima Headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.71,0:19:06.66,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,We are going to commence firing land-to-land missiles against the terrorists.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.66,0:19:09.58,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Major Kururugi, you are to prevent Zero from moving out of there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.46,0:19:12.33,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,He issued a death order to his subordinate?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.43,0:19:16.96,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Kururugi, you are...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.36,0:19:19.57,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,I can't agree with your methods.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.57,0:19:21.55,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, the only thing I can do is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.91,0:19:22.79,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.79,0:19:25.09,CG ON,Tohdoh,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move. You will be affected by the electronic field on the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.09,0:19:25.70,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.13,0:19:30.17,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,We will be using the Portman as escorts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.17,0:19:32.06,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Govenor-General, you should first...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.32,0:19:32.46,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.46,0:19:34.27,CG ON,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,You intend to blow up the Lancelot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.13,0:19:36.98,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Major Kururugi is preventing them from moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.41,0:19:39.65,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we can defeat Zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.65,0:19:43.55,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Who decided upon that operation? Kururugi Suzaku is my knight!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.10,0:19:46.38,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,This is a level-one order.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.38,0:19:48.52,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,The withdrawal of the order requires a position above governor-general
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.52,0:19:51.79,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,or the consent of more than three general-class personnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.05,0:19:54.82,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, who is the one who issued the order?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.82,0:19:56.29,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Connect a line for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.75,0:19:59.34,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,This is a level-one order, Vice Governor-General Euphemia.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.59,0:20:02.68,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Step aside!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.97,0:20:03.72,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Vice Governor-General!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.20,0:20:08.13,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Inform the base that there's the danger that I might be caught in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.13,0:20:09.93,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Even if that happens, are they still going to issue the order to fire?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.35,0:20:12.64,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,There should be a limit to your willfulness!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.64,0:20:14.79,CG ON,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,Erm, if Princess Euphemia is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.79,0:20:16.86,CG ON,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,It might be useless even with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.86,0:20:18.65,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Confirmation of missiles approaching!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.98,0:20:19.51,CG ON,Tohdoh,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.82,0:20:24.22,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Zero, I'm coming to save you now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.62,0:20:26.78,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.75,0:20:29.63,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,If this goes on, you will die!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.63,0:20:31.13,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really fine with that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.54,0:20:35.79,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Major Kururugi, this isn't a meaningless sacrifice!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.79,0:20:40.08,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,We will be able to defeat, with certainty, the criminal Zero who committed the grave sin of rebelling against the country!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.08,0:20:43.38,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Your heroic deed will definitely be retold via different means forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.38,0:20:44.03,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.31,0:20:47.35,CG ON,Tohdoh,0000,0000,0000,,To all KnightMares, fire a shower of bullets at the missiles incoming from the right side!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.68,0:20:49.18,CG ON,Tohdoh,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter if you use up all your ammunition!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.14,0:20:55.25,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Suzaku, let go of Zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.25,0:20:59.86,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,I am... I am...  Kallen Stadtfeld from the student council!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.86,0:21:01.11,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.24,0:21:06.53,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Suzaku, you can't die yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.81,0:21:09.60,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Soldiers must obey their orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.60,0:21:12.02,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph! Because it's easier that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.02,0:21:13.22,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Submitting to orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.96,0:21:15.73,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,What do {\i1}you{\i0} want?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.73,0:21:16.63,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.63,0:21:19.04,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,I decided upon this! This is my rule...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.74,0:21:32.14,CG ON,Rakshata,0000,0000,0000,,The Float System...? I'm bested.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.23,0:21:38.39,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,That's... Elder Brother's Avalon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.90,0:21:48.97,CG ON,Tohdoh,0000,0000,0000,,W-What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.62,0:21:54.68,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Suzaku, you will really die if this goes on!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.68,0:21:55.96,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Better than breaking rules!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.27,0:21:58.07,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,You unreasonable fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.77,0:23:49.19,CG Preview,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,My Geass is a power used to control people.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.44,0:23:52.11,CG Preview,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,No one is able to betray me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.11,0:23:54.49,CG Preview,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Also, the target who is given an order,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.00,0:23:59.80,CG Preview,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,his own morals, thoughts, and emotions will all be trampled.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.80,0:24:02.10,CG Preview,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Even though all of that was clear to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.87,0:24:04.48,CG Preview,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I made Suzaku...
